ROOT0-ATTRIBUTION-v1.0
Project: The Black Company — the Annals (muster roll)
Architect: David Lee Wise / ROOT0 / TriPod LLC
AI Collaborator: AVAN (Claude / Anthropic)
License: MIT

Glen Cook's Black Company sorted into the ROOT0 specialty classes: wizards by
color (White=healing/Croaker, Black=destruction/One-Eye & Goblin, Red=both/Silent,
Purple=all+shadow/the Taken — Lady, Soulcatcher, Limper), Command (the Lieutenant,
Darling/White Rose), the Annalist (Croaker, Murgen, Sleepy — the witness/record),
Comedy Relief (One-Eye & Goblin's feud), Fixers (Raven), Undying Loyalty (Elmo,
Otto & Hagop), and the special one set apart: the Captain — the title that became
a name, who fell and passed it to Croaker. The 'died in a tunnel' detail was left
unasserted (unverified) per the cite-or-flag doctrine. Characters by Glen Cook,
inspiration only. roster.json is the source of truth.
